headline: United States Laptop Market Report 2025-2033, Competitive Analysis of Acer, Apple, ASUSTeK, Dell, HP Development, Huawei,  LG, and Lenovo

headline: Vaudit Surpasses $1 Billion in Digital Ads Audited in 2025 and $100 Million in Refunds Processed for Global Brands Including Accenture, HP, Panasonic, and Volkswagen
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, December 03, 2025--Vaudit, the world’s first AI-driven Refund Engine for digital advertising, today announced that in 2025 it has officially audited more than $1 billion in annualized ad spend and processed over $100 million in refunds for global brands.
